{"tid":1060983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你父母或屋企人同你講過最感動既說話","createTime":"2019-03-14T05:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T09:37:55.000Z","uid":184957,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5198bd9d635328ba6c5d703440ad13e48710ae6c","tid":1060983,"uid":184957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"早兩日有人分享左最難聽既說話 <br />\n想聽下你地屋企人係你有事時候係點樣support你地<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得有啲令人難過既父母<br />\n反而以後做人父母會覺得自己更加得心應手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好遺憾分享唔到 ：一句support從來都沒有過<br />\n有無人分享下 袋定錢落袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ba13578a0f05fa0c34339e355007859e6d9d34","tid":1060983,"uid":177193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"第日老豆幫你俾首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da920896a53ccc7f2cd88a008a420c5b1b48687e","tid":1060983,"uid":73002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"我父母從來都冇點樣講過啲咩說話係支持我嘅決定，反而成日都否定我<br />\n唯一感動嘅事只係老母以前講過屋企人有今生冇來世，要好好珍惜，我而家係好珍惜我阿妹，同埋部份屋企人，但係唔會特別珍惜老母，因為由細到大佢都冇做過任何嘢去十卜我，細細個會因為一啲好少嘅事，例如唔想返興趣班，或者考試要溫書嗰陣想休息吓，都會俾佢打，我睇唔出佢係點樣珍惜我"},{"pid":"fbb4220bc927e62f7d28f9da0e073b89b33f44fe","tid":1060983,"uid":153329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"講就冇，行動就有<br />\n拎左幾十萬本比我做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27ee03142fe92af5a9f0c4cac338b9a3abcde81","tid":1060983,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"你搞到我好冇臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f17b0c29ba9460b4497a6d787d07c5b090efe84","tid":1060983,"uid":203474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"今晚返嚟食飯？ <br />\n<br />\n飲唔飲湯啊？<br />\n<br />\n一諗到屋企個老母等緊自己，就好唔捨得佢捱餓等我，即刻狗衝返屋企。"},{"pid":"7bc533f2ca327bb12e2ce216fbc70c85e9726512","tid":1060983,"uid":184957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7f17b0c29ba9460b4497a6d787d07c5b090efe84","tid":1060983,"uid":203474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"今晚返嚟食飯？ <br />\n<br />\n飲唔飲湯啊？<br />\n<br />\n一諗到屋企個老母等緊自己，就好唔捨得佢捱餓等我，即刻狗衝返屋企。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"幸福  但真係唔係基本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a7f7f67080d13b3af6d518e7870737dbdecc1f","tid":1060983,"uid":151065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"我父母唔會言語上表達感情<br />\n但佢地真係我想要乜都俾我<br />\n由細到大想玩嘅興趣佢地完全dum本<br />\n亦都冇話大個要養家還俾佢地<br />\n而係搵自己鍾意嘅嘢做"},{"pid":"1e21d71d761ff5d9cc2c60ec8be50daf633d59ea","tid":1060983,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"借你D糧黎出糧俾人<br />\n<br />\n我感動萬分<br />\n終於唔洗擔心佢老左要照顧佢"},{"pid":"dce70c8279f5ecd5bfed8a8a5c1fb5dcd4d3a677","tid":1060983,"uid":203474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bc533f2ca327bb12e2ce216fbc70c85e9726512","tid":1060983,"uid":184957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7f17b0c29ba9460b4497a6d787d07c5b090efe84","tid":1060983,"uid":203474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"今晚返嚟食飯？ <br />\n<br />\n飲唔飲湯啊？<br />\n<br />\n一諗到屋企個老母等緊自己，就好唔捨得佢捱餓等我，即刻狗衝返屋企。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"幸福  但真係唔係基本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"所以我已經學識珍惜真心愛自己既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aea5f1fd6d329b89b18246f2550dd4a0d4a037","tid":1060983,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"生舊叉燒好過生你"},{"p